{"audioUrl": "", "duration": 52.005, "paragraphs": [{"id": "p1", "sentences": [{"id": "p1s1", "text": "Minha jornada pela feira local sempre come\u00e7a com o aroma doce de morangos frescos.", "boundaries": [{"text": "Minha ", "start": 0.0, "end": 0.255}, {"text": "jornada ", "start": 0.302, "end": 0.813}, {"text": "pela ", "start": 0.848, "end": 1.022}, {"text": "feira ", "start": 1.08, "end": 1.3}, {"text": "local ", "start": 1.347, "end": 1.718}, {"text": "sempre ", "start": 1.811, "end": 2.136}, {"text": "come\u00e7a ", "start": 2.171, "end": 2.612}, {"text": "com ", "start": 2.659, "end": 2.798}, {"text": "o ", "start": 2.844, "end": 2.868}, {"text": "aroma ", "start": 2.926, "end": 3.239}, {"text": "doce ", "start": 3.309, "end": 3.646}, {"text": "de ", "start": 3.704, "end": 3.762}, {"text": "morangos ", "start": 3.808, "end": 4.203}, {"text": "frescos.", "start": 4.261, "end": 4.969}]}, {"id": "p1s2", "text": "S\u00e1bado de manh\u00e3, bem cedo, as barracas est\u00e3o repletas de cores vibrantes e rostos simp\u00e1ticos.", "boundaries": [{"text": "S\u00e1bado ", "start": 5.561, "end": 5.956}, {"text": "de ", "start": 6.002, "end": 6.06}, {"text": "manh\u00e3, ", "start": 6.107, "end": 6.502}, {"text": "bem ", "start": 6.536, "end": 6.757}, {"text": "cedo, ", "start": 6.827, "end": 7.419}, {"text": "as ", "start": 7.593, "end": 7.721}, {"text": "barracas ", "start": 7.779, "end": 8.243}, {"text": "est\u00e3o ", "start": 8.29, "end": 8.51}, {"text": "repletas ", "start": 8.545, "end": 9.056}, {"text": "de ", "start": 9.102, "end": 9.172}, {"text": "cores ", "start": 9.23, "end": 9.543}, {"text": "vibrantes ", "start": 9.601, "end": 10.263}, {"text": "e ", "start": 10.379, "end": 10.495}, {"text": "rostos ", "start": 10.553, "end": 10.983}, {"text": "simp\u00e1ticos.", "start": 11.006, "end": 11.9}]}, {"id": "p1s3", "text": "Adoro conferir a sele\u00e7\u00e3o diversificada de vegetais org\u00e2nicos e queijos artesanais.", "boundaries": [{"text": "Adoro ", "st